OL,3,CTroubles legacy cost over #6m so far,
OL,4,Cleading think tank says
OL,6,FThe cost of dealing with Northern
OL,7,FIreland's troubled past is set to be
OL,8,Fconsiderably more than #2 billion, a
OL,9,FUK think tank has estimated.
OL,11,FThe Policy Exchange has put the cost
OL,12,Fof inquiries, court cases, inquests
OL,13,Fand compensation payouts so far at
OL,14,Fbetween #840 million and #1.4 billion.
OL,16,FThey also estimated a further #1.3
OL,17,Fbillion will be incurred in the
OL,18,Ffuture, leading to a total cost in
OL,19,Fconnection with the Troubles as
OL,20,F"between #2.2 billion and #2.7
OL,21,Fbillion".
