OL,6,FIn a foreword to the Policy Exchange
OL,7,Fpaper, former Conservative chancellor
OL,8,FJeremy Hunt claimed the approach of
OL,9,Fthe Government to the legacy of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland's past "appears at
OL,11,Ftimes to be being dictated by a
OL,12,Fmaximalist approach to legalism,
OL,13,Fwithout regard to the underlying
OL,14,Fbenefits or costs".
OL,16,FHe claimed this approach is "wrong,
OL,17,Fnot least when short-term penny
OL,18,Fpinching has lost the UK a #450
OL,19,Fmillion vaccine manufacturing plant
OL,20,Finvestment from AstraZeneca".
