OL,3,CTroubles legacy cost over #6m so far,
OL,4,Cleading think tank says
OL,6,F"When every line of additional
OL,7,Fdepartmental spending must run the
OL,8,FTreasury gauntlet, is it right that
OL,9,Fthere should be no such checks on the
OL,10,Ftotal cost of inquiries whether
OL,11,Fconcerning Northern Ireland or indeed
OL,12,Fanywhere else?" he said.
OL,14,F"If the additional sums being
OL,15,Fcommitted by this Government to legacy
OL,16,Fmatters were genuinely helping to
OL,17,Fbring about peace and reconciliation,
OL,18,Fthe country would pay them cheerfully.
